contacts.help:
### To make things work you should:
### In personal chat:
 - start conversation with bot [@ExampleMoiraBot](https://t.me/ExampleMoiraBot);
 - execute command `/start`;
 - type your login in above field as `@login`.

### In group chat:
 - invite bot [@ExampleMoiraBot](https://t.me/ExampleMoiraBot) into chat;
 - execute command `/start@ExampleMoiraBot`;
 - bot will send you chat id, you should type it without extra characters in above field.

### In channel:
 - add bot [@ExampleMoiraBot](https://t.me/ExampleMoiraBot) into channel;
 - promote bot as channel administrator;
 - type channel name in above field as `#channel`.
